<i>#Hear those sleigh bells</i>
<i>jinglejangle #</i>

20:04.403 --> 20:06.462
<i>#Oh, what a beautiful sight #</i>

20:06.572 --> 20:08.767
<i>#Sojump in bed</i>
<i>and cover your head #</i>

20:08.874 --> 20:11.434
<i>#'Cause Santa Claus comes tonight #</i>

20:15.514 --> 20:17.414
<i>[Knocking]</i>

20:17.516 --> 20:20.974
<i>And to my surprise, he ended up teaching me</i>
<i>something pretty important too.</i>

20:21.086 --> 20:24.613
Merry Christmas, Joy.

20:24.723 --> 20:28.250
Oh, my God.
You got our old refrigerator back.

20:28.360 --> 20:31.852
We don't have to keep the kids' antibiotics
up against the air conditioner anymore.

20:31.964 --> 20:34.728
<i>He taught me that being generous</i>
<i>to someone who's done you wrong...</i>

20:34.833 --> 20:36.733
<i>can be the best kind</i>
<i>of charity there is.</i>

20:39.705 --> 20:41.900
Oh. It's empty.

20:43.642 --> 20:46.543
That's okay. It's still nice.
Come on in.

20:46.645 --> 20:48.306
<i>#Hear those sleigh bells</i>
<i>jinglejangle #</i>

20:48.413 --> 20:51.007
<i>#Oh, what a beautiful sight #</i>

20:51.116 --> 20:53.380
<i>#Sojump in bed</i>
